model

Class ValidatedExam

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.ValidatedExam

  • public class ValidatedExam
extends java.lang.Object
    ValidatedExam contains informations related to an exam that has been input into a report.

    This state information includes:

    • The validated exam ID
    • The report ID
    • The exam external name
    • The validated CFU number
    • The validation procedure note
    Author:
    Gianluca Rossi
    See Also:
    Report
